'''Marburg disease'''

# {{pathology}} A viral infection characterised by a high [[fever]], [[encephalitis]], [[diarrhea]], vomiting, and severe bleeding from bodily orifices, and which is often fatal.

====Synonyms====
* [[green monkey disease]]
* [[Marburg fever]]
* [[Marburg hemorrhagic fever]]
* [[Marburg virus disease]]